 Britten</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/gabriella-sborgi/" rel="tag">Gabriella Sborgi</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/john-daszak/" rel="tag">John Daszak</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/jonathan-webb/" rel="tag">Jonathan Webb</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/opera-lirica/" rel="tag">Opera lirica</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/rebecca-leggett/" rel="tag">Rebecca Leggett</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/sara-hershkowitz/" rel="tag">Sara Hershkowitz</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/teatro-goldoni-di-firenze/" rel="tag">Teatro Goldoni di Firenze</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/the-turn-of-the-screw/" rel="tag">The turn of the screw</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/theo-lally/" rel="tag">Theo Lally</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/yana-kleyn/" rel="tag">Yana Kleyn</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="78 Festival Maggio Musicale Fiorentino, Benedetto Sicca, Benjamin Britten, Gabriella Sborgi, John Daszak, Jonathan Webb, Opera lirica, Rebecca Leggett, Sara Hershkowitz, Teatro Goldoni di Firenze, The turn of the screw, Theo Lally, Yana Kleyn"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/9ba640a7ac7b6985c46cf498c1470596" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/Nicola-Lischi-116x150.jpg" width="77" height="100" alt="Nicola Lischi" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Nicola Lischi"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/nicola-lischi/">View all articles by Nicola Lischi</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2015/05/la-city-of-birmingham-symphony-orchestra-a-madrid-2/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> La City of Birmingham Symphony Orchestra a Madrid (2)</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2015/05/limmortalita-di-orfeo-ed-euridice-al-san-carlo-di-napoli-la-danza-di-karole-armitage/" rel="next">Limmortalit di &#8220;Orfeo ed Euridice&#8221;al Teatro San Carlo di Napoli. La Danza di Karole Armitage. <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><div id="respond" class="comment-respond"><h3 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title">Lascia un commento <small><a rel="nofollow" id="cancel-comment-reply-link" href="/2015/05/firenze-teatro-goldoni-the-turn-of-the-screw/#respond" style="display:none;">Annulla risposta</a></small></h3><form action="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-comments-post.php" method="post" id="commentform" class="comment-form"><p class="comment-notes"><span id="email-notes">Il tuo indirizzo email non sar pubblicato.</span> I campi obbligatori sono contrassegnati <span class="required">*</span></p><p class="comment-form-comment"><label for="comment">Commento</label><textarea id="comment" name="comment" cols="45" rows="8" maxlength="65525" aria-required="true" required="required"></textarea></p><p class="comment-form-author"><label for="author">Nome <span class="required">*</span></label> <input id="author" name="author" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="245" aria-required=\'tr